            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">What Happens Next?</h3>
            <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-300 text-left">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-semibold mr-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  1
                </div>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-white">Quick Response:</strong> I'll email you back within 24 hours to acknowledge your inquiry and ask any clarifying questions.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-semibold mr-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  2
                </div>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-white">Project Discussion:</strong> We'll schedule a free 30-minute consultation to discuss your project in detail.
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-semibold mr-4 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  3
                </div>
                <div>
                  <strong class="text-white">Custom Proposal:</strong> I'll provide a detailed proposal with timeline, deliverables, and pricing.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a 
              href="/"
              class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors"
            >
              Back to Home
            </a>
            <a 
              href="/projects"
